author: Lindsey Stirling
description:
You can either tailor your life to fit where you’re at, or tailor your life to grow to where you want to be. When I started touring I wasn’t a dancers, and I wasn’t an aerialist, but I’ve trained and worked incredibly hard year after year to build my skills and strength so I could create the show of my dreams.
